VExcellent buy!
p68
sg5
VI'm going to keep it nice and simple. I bought this headphone a week ago here on Amazon and LOVE it! It has exceeded my expectations.1. it's very light and the ear pods are very comfortable. the headphones are well balanced once worn.2. the battery life is great! I charged it the full 24 hours initially and am now going to use it until it completely drains. Three of these cycles should ensure the best battery performance as memory effect will be reduced in subsequent chargings.3. the range so far has been great. I can use it all over my house without any deadspots. I've even gone to the end of the driveway without any problems....soon I'll try farther out to see what she/he can do!4. I have not had any of the interference issues some have had, but it can be easily corrected with a frequency adjustment5. All in all, I think this is one of the best items I've ever bought on Amazon and I find myself using it all the time.
