VI bought these headphones for my grandfather because his hearing is poor and we don't want him to blow his TV speakers out, plus we want to be able to hear. He has had many different sets of headphones and all of them are collecting dust in a box somewhere. This set is different for a few reasons. First of all, they was a lot easier to plug in to his DVR then some of the others have been, of course those ones were from many years ago and technology has come a long way. The next point he liked was the charging dock and how easy it is to use since he doesn't have to plug them in or anything like that. The tuning is easy and the sound quality is fantastic. He can actually hear his TV and they aren't turned all the way up and that is really a plus for all of us. He also likes that they just sit on top of his ear because the ones that encapsulate his ears just do not fit. The only complaint that he has is that they do not have a volume adjustment for each ear individually. His right ear is worse than this left and so what is good for the right is a little to loud for the left. That is why I give this product a 4 star because that might one day be enough to get him to stop using them. However, these are currently a hit with him and that is important to me. I think they are a good product and a good purchase.
