VAs stated they're hot on the ears... FIXED !!
p827
sg5
VI was really pleased with these headphones but as many others have stated, they do make your ears sweat. Simple solution though. Change these to around the ear phones using these.... beyerdynamic EDT 250 V..... sold on amazon, just do a search. Although they are made to fit Sony MDR V-6 phones they will fit on these nicely.  Remove each side of the RS120 pads by twisting a little to the left on each side. Remove all the foam pieces until all you have left is the plastic grids for each side. In the beyerdynamic kit there are two fiber like oval washers, throw em away.Just lay the black, round foam piece on top of the plastic grid and install the earpads by stretching the lip over the plastic grids. This will hold the round, black foam piece in. WOW, HEAVEN !! So much more comfortable. I would have given these headphones 5 stars if I wouldn't have had to do the modification.
