VI work in an open bull pen office with 300 people. I sit right next to the phone bank for customer service. Headphones are essential to my working sanity. These headphones are great. I can wear them all day with no battery issues, no earlobe pain, no sweaty ears, and no need to continuously adjust the fit. I put them on, I turn them on, I tune out the world for hours. The recharge base is super easy to use -- just set the headphones on it. No plugging in each time or changing batteries. I set mine behind my monitor so I don't have to see it or have it in the way. I'm not an audiophile, so I can't comment on the finer points of audio quality, but for your average techy geek who likes electronics and wants something that sounds good (like me) these fit the bill. Haven't had any interference in the signal. Haven't had any issues whatsoever. Very pleased.
