VIntermittent reception and poorly designed wiring
p1926
sg5
VThe sound from the unit is excellent. The headphones are comfortable.  But no matter where I place the receiver it cuts out every 3-5 minutes for 2-30 seconds at a time.  It's tolerable so I'm going to keep it and maybe try some more locations.The unit also has inconvenient, poorly designed power and input connections.  The power wire is fixed in the unit.  When I want to move the unit I have to unplug the power wire from the source, pull it out from my cabinet and rerun it back to the power source rather than just unplugging it from the unit and reconnecting the power wire at the new receiver location.  The input wire is very difficult to plug into the unit and to remove it.  I had to use needle nose plier to get it out.  I wonder if the people who makes these ever use them themselves.
